    "body": "I completely agree with you.  In the past I would have suggested adding more miner witnesses, somewhere between 2-5, in addition to expanding the rotating constant witnesses.  This could better distribute rewards, and encourage mining as more than just a costly hobby.  The current domination of the mining queue by one (possibly two) users makes this a bad idea, though.",
